snippet.textDisplay:
Ali Zafar is truly rocking the Coke Studio S08, both with "Rockstar" and "Ae Dil"! They are not just catchy numbers, but truly engaging lyrics and composition. 

This is the first time I heard Sara Haider and must say she remarkably sang this and even her backing vocals add a punch! 

Overall Ali Zafar truly showed how diverse a singer he's - from the soulful Dastaan-e-Ishq to these songs...
